N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 342.9 - Withdrawing option elections; choosing a new option

State Regulations

An election of an option may be withdrawn or a new option may
be chosen until the first day of the month following the effective date of
retirement. Notes
